SUMMARY:Rethinking European Security in an Age of Uncertainty
DESCRIPTION:Russia's war against Ukraine and shifting global power balanc
 es have forced Europe to confront new strategic realities. This talk asse
 sses Europe's support for Ukraine\, the future of transatlantic cooperati
 on\, and the diplomatic tools available to European leaders in an increas
 ingly uncertain world.Read more about Dr. Sus. (https://www.monikasus.com
 /)
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p><span data-olk-copy-source="MessageBody">
 Russia's war against Ukraine and shifting global power balances have forc
 ed Europe to confront new strategic realities. This talk assesses Europe'
 s support for Ukraine\, the future of transatlantic cooperation\, and the
  diplomatic tools available to European leaders in an increasingly uncert
 ain world.</span></p><p><strong><em><a href="https://www.monikasus.com/" 
 target="_blank" rel="noopener">Read more about Dr. Sus.</a></em></strong>
 </p>
