 ng IU Jacobs School faculty and students\, part of the IU-Taiwan Collabor
 ations in Music Project\, followed by a reception for registered attendee
 s in the Atrium.&#160\;</p><p>  Alexander Tah-Ray Yui is Taiwan's Represe
 ntative to the United States\, a role he assumed in December 2023. He has
