SUMMARY:Career Studio: Summer Experience Challenge
DESCRIPTION:Need ideas of ways you can gain experience this summer? Join 
 us in the Career Studio where you will collaborate with other students to
  solve real-world career scenarios\, explore multiple experience routes\,
  and identify the opportunities that best support your personal career go
 als.&#160\;You'll leave the workshop with a list of real\, impactful thin
 gs you can pursue this summer (that are tailored to your interests!)\, st
 eps to get involved with each opportunity\, and an excitement for what's 
 next.&#160\;Peer coaches will be present to answer any career or academic
  questions you might have.&#160\;
