 \, community partners\, and students from IU Bloomington to celebrate and
  recognize achievements in community engaged learning. We explore best pr
 actices in CEL and teaching and how community-engagement elevates profess
 ional growth and research. Connect with peers\, share insights\, and shap
 e the future of education.</p><p>  The structure of the conference is a h
 alf-day with structured space for networking\, conversation\, and worksho
