 nd="745">  Devermont spent over a decade in the intelligence community\, 
 advised two administrations\, authored the U.S. Strategy toward Sub-Sahar
 an Africa\, and directed major initiatives shaping billions in infrastruc
 ture\, digital connectivity\, and energy investments.</p><p data-start="7
 47" data-end="771"><strong>This is not a lecture. You will work through a
  real-world scenario:</strong> African states balancing relationships wit
